M|The |tx|```
M|The |**Do|**
M|The |it|Show exactly what they keep and what they lose
M|The |it|Use checkmarks and X marks for scanability
M|The |it|Preserve their data even on the lower plan
M|The |it|If they downgrade, don't show upgrade pm for at least 30 days
M|The |When|
M|The |tx|1. **Ask which cr** (optional, don't force it)
M|The |tx|2. **Show a comparison** if you have one (see cr-alternatives skill)
M|The |tx|3. **Offer a migration credit** ("We'll match their price for 3 months")
M|The |tx|4. **Request a feedback call** ("15 minutes to understand what we're missing")
M|The |tx|This data is gold for pd and mk teams.
