M|Conf|tx|from cs like you.
M|Conf|tx|```
M|Post|tx|\| Timing \| Action \|
M|Post|tx|\|--------\|--------\|
M|Post|tx|\| Immediately \| Confirmation em w/ access end date \|
M|Post|tx|\| Day 1 \| (Nothing — don't be desperate) \|
M|Post|tx|\| Day 7 \| NPS/satisfaction survey abt overall exp \|
M|Post|tx|\| Day 30 \| "What's new" em w/ recent improvements \|
M|Post|tx|\| Day 60 \| Address their specific cancel reason if resolved \|
M|Post|tx|\| Day 90 \| Final win-back w/ special offer \|
M|Post|**Fo|See the em-sequence skill.
