M|FTC |it|Cancellation must be as easy as signup
M|FTC |it|Cannot require a phone call to cancel if signup was online
M|FTC |it|Cannot add excessive steps to discourage cancellation
M|FTC |it|Save offers are allowed but "continue cancelling" must be clear
M|GDPR|it|Inform us abt data retention period post-cancel
M|GDPR|it|Offer data export before account deletion
M|GDPR|it|Honor deletion requests within 30 days
M|GDPR|it|Don't use post-cancel data for mk w/o consent
M|Gene|it|Always show a clear path to complete cancellation
M|Gene|it|Never hide the cancel button (dark pattern)
M|Gene|it|Process cancellation even if save flow has er
M|Gene|it|Confirm cancellation w/ em receipt